summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of West Sixty-fourth Street, from 22nd Avenue N. W. to 26th Avenue N. W. in the City of Seattle, by resurfacing under Ordinance No. 25742, creating Local Improvement District No. 2432 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing the delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
